  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare if the effect of levobupivacaine on autonomic nervous
      system smaller than that of bupivacaine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Obtain the heart rate variability (in means and standard deviation, including the high
      frequency, low frequency and its ratio) data of before and after spinal anesthesia with ECG
      (and Heart Rate Variability Analyzer) in 2 groups. Meanwhile, record the blood pressure on
      each subject.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
